| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3161 — Recovery Inhibition (safepay)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 03c6d329-24cb-5cbc-b85c-ccc60954c9ac"
